  "title": "Marketing Executive (Cleaning Industry)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Business Development</strong><br />• Source and secure new cleaning contracts (commercial, residential, industrial, schools, condos, etc.)<br />• Conduct site surveys and understand client cleaning requirements<br />• Prepare quotations and proposals for clients<br />• Maintain and grow strong customer relationships<br />• Plan sales strategies to achieve monthly and yearly targets</p><p><strong>Tender & Project Submission</strong><br />• Prepare tender documents including pricing, costing, manpower deployment, and job scope<br />• Work closely with operations team to ensure accurate site information<br />• Compile necessary documents (company profile, NEA licence, track record, certificates)<br />• Submit tenders through Gebiz, Vendors@Gov, and private portals<br />• Ensure all tender deadlines are met<br />• Assist in attending tender briefings and site show-rounds</p>",
